---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, "");
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about Ashfaq Ur Rahman, a recent Computer Science Engineering graduate focused on web development, clean UI/UX, and data-driven problem solving."
>
  <div class="container" style="padding-top: calc(var(--nav-height) + var(--space-16)); padding-bottom: var(--space-24);">
    <div class="about-layout">

      <main class="about-main">
        <h1 class="about-title">About me</h1>

        <div class="prose">
          <p>
            I'm Ashfaq Ur Rahman, a recent Computer Science Engineering graduate based in Khammam, India,
            with an aggregate CGPA of 7.97. I'm passionate about building modern web experiences and using
            data to solve real problems. My interests are centered around web development, clean and
            user-focused UI/UX, and data analysis that helps people and businesses make better decisions.
          </p>

          <p>
            I enjoy creating responsive websites using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, with a strong focus on
            clarity, usability, and maintainable structure. I like interfaces that are simple, professional,
            and purposeful — not just visually clean, but also easy to use and accessible across devices.
          </p>

          <p>
            Alongside frontend development, I have hands-on knowledge of Python for data analysis,
            especially with Pandas and NumPy, as well as tools like Power BI, Excel, and SQL. I'm interested
            in transforming raw data into meaningful insights, such as identifying which areas are lagging,
            where performance can be improved, and which products, teams, or processes are generating more profit.
          </p>

          <h2>What I'm working on</h2>

          <p>
            Right now, I'm focused on strengthening my portfolio through practical projects that combine
            software development and analytics. I've been working on projects related to resume analysis,
            dashboards, and portfolio development, while also improving my problem-solving, project structure,
            and deployment skills.
          </p>

          <p>
            I'm actively looking for an opportunity where I can begin my career, contribute to real-world
            products, and continue learning in a professional environment. I'm especially interested in
            roles where I can apply both technical development skills and analytical thinking to create
            useful, decision-driven solutions.
          </p>

          <h2>What I bring</h2>

          <p>
            I bring a combination of technical curiosity, responsibility, and a strong willingness to learn.
            I like understanding a problem clearly before building a solution, and I try to keep my work
            organized, practical, and focused on outcomes. Whether I'm designing a clean interface or
            analyzing a dataset, I aim to create work that is clear, useful, and professional.
          </p>

          
          <h2>Outside academics and work</h2>

          <p>
            Outside of projects and study, I enjoy exploring new technologies, improving my practical coding
            skills, and learning how strong products are designed and built. I'm motivated by growth, real
            problem-solving, and the idea of building a career where technology and analysis come together in a meaningful way.
          </p>

          <h2>How I work</h2>

          <p>
            I work best when I understand the goal clearly and can break the problem into smaller steps.
            I believe good work comes from planning well, paying attention to detail, and staying open to feedback.
          </p>

        </div>
      </main>


        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h2 class="sidebar-heading">Links</h2>
          <ul class="link-list" role="list">
            <li>
              <a href="https://github.com/ashfaq8121" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                GitHub &nearr;
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/ashfaq-ur-rahman-54832027b" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                LinkedIn &nearr;
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href={`${base}/rss.xml`}>
                RSS feed
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h2 class="sidebar-heading">Currently focused on</h2>
          <p class="sidebar-text">
            Building portfolio projects, improving data analytics skills, and preparing for entry-level software and data roles.
          </p>
        </div>
      </aside>
        
    <aside class="about-sidebar" aria-label="Skills and links">
      <div class="sidebar-card">
       <h2 class="sidebar-heading">Skills</h2>
     <div class="skills-tags">
       <span class="skill-tag">HTML</span>
       <span class="skill-tag">CSS</span>
       <span class="skill-tag">JavaScript</span>
       <span class="skill-tag">Responsive Web Design</span>
       <span class="skill-tag">Clean UI/UX Design</span>
       <span class="skill-tag">Python</span>
       <span class="skill-tag">Pandas</span>
       <span class="skill-tag">NumPy</span>
       <span class="skill-tag">Power BI</span>
       <span class="skill-tag">SQL</span>
       <span class="skill-tag">Excel</span>
       <span class="skill-tag">Data Analysis</span>
       <span class="skill-tag">Dashboard Building</span>
       <span class="skill-tag">GitHub</span>
       <span class="skill-tag">Cloudflare</span>
      </div>
      </div>
   </aside>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .about-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 18rem;
    }
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .about-sidebar {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .sidebar-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: var(--space-6);
  }

  .sidebar-heading {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }


  .link-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .link-list a {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .link-list a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }

  .sidebar-text {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .skills-group {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .skills-group:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .skills-category {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2) 0;
  }

  .skills-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-1-5);
  }

  .skill-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--color-surface-offset, rgba(0,0,0,0.05));
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    line-height: 1.4;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
</style>
